| Column Name              | Description               |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------- |
| referral_id              | Unique referral ID        |
| referral_source          | Source of referral        |
| referral_source_category | Category of referral      |
| referral_at              | Date referral created     |
| referrer_id              | User who referred         |
| referee_id               | Referred user             |
| referee_name             | Name of referred user     |
| referee_phone            | Phone number              |
| transaction_id           | Transaction ID            |
| transaction_status       | Status of payment         |
| transaction_type         | Type of transaction       |
| reward_value             | Reward amount             |
| is_business_logic_valid  | Whether referral is valid |
